The incident was reported at around 9pm on Thursday night, after four train carriages were destroyed in the fire. CAPE TOWN Authorities are investigating the circumstances around an apparent arson attack on a Metrorail train at Thornton Station.The incident was reported at around 9pm on Thursday night.Four train carriages were destroyed in the fire.No injuries were reported and services were not affected by the incident.(Edited by Masechaba Sefularo)